# cron 示例

## 每 5 分钟执行一次

```cron
*/5 * * * * /usr/bin/python3 /root/clawd/code/data-quality-word-report/cpa_token_uploader.py --config /root/.cpa_token_uploader.json >> /var/log/cpa_token_uploader.log 2>&1
```

## 每 1 分钟执行一次（仅在目录文件量很小且接口稳定时考虑）

```cron
* * * * * /usr/bin/python3 /root/clawd/code/data-quality-word-report/cpa_token_uploader.py --config /root/.cpa_token_uploader.json >> /var/log/cpa_token_uploader.log 2>&1
```

## 首次上线建议

先把配置里的：

- `delete_after_upload`: `false`

先观察几轮，确认上传正常，再改成：

- `delete_after_upload`: `true`

## 常用手动命令

### dry-run

```bash
python3 /root/clawd/code/data-quality-word-report/cpa_token_uploader.py --config /root/.cpa_token_uploader.json --dry-run
```

### 正式执行

```bash
python3 /root/clawd/code/data-quality-word-report/cpa_token_uploader.py --config /root/.cpa_token_uploader.json
```
